{"type": "article", "id": 19065, "title": "节日挂坠", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-15T09:27:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606142920RmiIuB7CqTx3t4cs.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t34 家来自纽约或洛杉矶的设计事务所为 MOCAD（Museum of Contemporary Art Detroit，底特律现代美术馆）设计了这些节日的装点。有带彩色纹理的石头、蓝色的气球、金属框、挂起来的盆景，总之每家事务所使用了不同的材料或元素，也以此代表自己的理念，比普通的装饰物多了一份艺术感，很适合挂在圣诞树上。<a href=\"http://paddle8.com/auction/shinolaworkof/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145735nhugWkw0B8YGLt9V.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145737OrQeZHkGRs9Ew0tX.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145737PHXinWqGlSB2FdML.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145738xow7XyVzYmFRbcuD.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261457385NIEhsup1boW7edv.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}